author: stoddard
msg: Performance: Add quick_handler hook. This hook is called at the
very beginning of the request processing before location_walk,
translate_name, etc.  This hook is useful for URI keyed content
caches like Mike Abbott's Quick Shortcut Cache.

author: wrowe
msg: Resolve the stdcall/cdecl ambiguity that caused Win2K to crash with the
set service description patch.  Also lighten the load (don't allocate
a handle) to get at the advapi32.dll we already statically link to.
